{"id": "1270615070577004618", "channel_id": "1270615070577004618", "type": 0, "author_id": "1231540652253253705", "author_name": "menoctus", "author_bot": false, "content": "> 大家好，這裡是難忘今宵攻略組，本期為大家帶來的是第14期「融災禁區」地圖。\n\n◆每兩週刷新獎勵與關卡，每個關卡只需要完成普通模式、困難或癲狂模式其中之一。\n\n◆經過毒地板（紫色格子）時，會扣除 血量上限 的約5%，也就是固定值。\n\n當踏入毒地板所扣除的血量被判定為致命傷害，則觸發死亡抵抗/復活確認。\n\n◆同一關卡的各級警示地圖都相同。\n\n▼▼▼\n\n【第1波】無光之境 - 間隙地圖（混沌5，深海3，血肉1，超維7）\n【第2波】特遣紀錄 - 索蕾爾「薔薇禮贊」-淑女指南 地圖\n【第3波】如圖\n【第4波】意識潛遊 - 奧吉爾「騎士的願望」-曲終人散 地圖\n【第5波】意識潛遊-阿格里帕「迷宮的盡頭」地圖", "timestamp": "2024-08-07T05:30:39.712000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-08-07T05:32:27.406000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1270615074582564865", "filename": "14.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 2748879, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1270615070577004618/1270615074582564865/14.jpg?ex=69fb7ac0&is=69fa2940&hm=ef9a0d965d40df40bf83f936759a490e2646649ade232000506717846b66039a&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1270615070577004618", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "關卡地圖「融災禁區」總覽ⅩⅣ", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1283686881858420777", "1181143392739147778"]}
{"id": "1270604062840324116", "channel_id": "1270604062840324116", "type": 0, "author_id": "299947644208414720", "author_name": "cs001092", "author_bot": false, "content": "终于打到375了1\n我是54321反着打\n第5关，第一次打，感觉能强杀精英不用用绕路，就重开一把\n造物够胡，没爪未必打得爆的了。镜像，相机和火柴盒也帮了不少\n不然血卖不够多也会悲剧\n\n第4关，镜像到偷力或许容易一点（鲨鱼启度得够）\n\n第3关，如果借泥工的24或许容易点，不过我已经用在第5关了。。。\n\n第2关，好在boss没有叠力，血回快，基本是能挺过去的\n\n第1关，之前打350的时候感觉回血够快，感觉能直接开局就开王，加上这轮融灾4关打完留了些回血命轮，就直接上了（混沌开局银造物也一定程度上帮了不少）", "timestamp": "2024-08-07T04:46:55.263000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1270604063355961375", "filename": "Screenshot_20240807_120512_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 181858, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1270604062840324116/1270604063355961375/Screenshot_20240807_120512_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg?ex=69fb707f&is=69fa1eff&hm=c4f19b2ebbf94794b7e1d372761e0ef3d5c86d763fe76eede44dce527f626782&"}, {"id": "1270604063805014147", "filename": "Screenshot_20240807_120501_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 183137, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1270604062840324116/1270604063805014147/Screenshot_20240807_120501_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg?ex=69fb707f&is=69fa1eff&hm=02ba7ab664f6e55ea35b9f89846d2c83d0eb9e39c27c31bcb512df64676799ad&"}, {"id": "1270604064165593150", "filename": "Screenshot_20240807_120448_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 183637, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1270604062840324116/1270604064165593150/Screenshot_20240807_120448_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg?ex=69fb707f&is=69fa1eff&hm=a06fbcda569ee684869d00563cf8843d20c7342db94cea130629b746d2461b55&"}, {"id": "1270604064543211520", "filename": "Screenshot_20240807_120435_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 193532, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1270604062840324116/12